items.name: Auditorium
items.description:
中文简介在后方

Base Model: RealisticVision_v20

Tirrger tag is auditorium, Use prompts like view to stage, view to seat, side view, blue chairs, end stage/central stage/black box theatre, cool/warm/dark/light colors, dark colored flooring, stripe ceiling, hanging equipment, light, spotlight.... to guild this lora.

Controlnet is allways reccomended if you wish to use it in real life design, much more efficiency in generating the right spacial structure, I personally have tested it and get some interesting feedback. tip: Use lineart or scrible model depend on how bad you drawing is, which should catch the basic assumption of the stage, stalls, balconies, and something that looks like chairs.

The model is trained on 200+ images of built or unbuilt aditoriums.

Please rate the model or post you image if you have tried this, really appreciate any feedback.

底模选用 RealisticVision_v20，提示词见上方。

使用 Controlnet 可以有效提高生成图片空间关系正确的概率，尤其当你是用来进行真实项目设计的时候。我试用过得到的反馈还是挺有意思的。tip：你的手稿应该要反映舞台、池座、楼座的大关系，座位可以用一些看起来像那么回事的线条表示。

训练使用了两百多张观众厅的照片或渲染图，主要是照片。

试用过的网友欢迎评论打分哟，期待你们的反馈。

Edit:
So i forgot some images that i use for the preview using control net when looking for pose or propotions, Here some guide to use ControlNet

  • Go towards extensions tabs and install this extension, https://github.com/Mikubill/sd-webui-controlnet

  • Download ControlNet model (https://huggingface.co/lllyasviel/ControlNet/tree/main/models) (recomended the openpose one) and place it inside sd-webui-controlnet/models extension folder

  • After installing, a tab named Control Net should be appeared in txt2img or img2img

  • Open the tab and use this image as a guidelines, pretty much use openpose preprocessor and openpose model then place the image that you want to use inside the tab.

  • Sometimes this method not working, you can use openpose stickman instead, here my collection of openpose stickman (set preprocessor to none like this)

  • Then just generate images like usual, just leave the ControlNet enabled. the image should resemble the pose

items.name: Periwinkle
items.description:
What is Periwinkle?

Periwinkle is an anime model with a unique blend or aesthetic. A tool to assist artists and writers for creating illustration for graphic novels, manga, kids' book, promotional arts and more. I personally use this model for my works, which is well suited on one of my styles. Regarding text prompts, just be versatile and let your imagination flow. And, just like most models it also has few issues with the hands, which can be easily mitigated with this model's inpainting (download separately) or some embeddings. (I still have other models, for some specific arts, yet to be released. Your support will go a long way, and a cup of coffee will keep me awake for many nights. Thank you in advance!)

This version of Periwinkle does not include a VAE because the goal is for art versatility, wherein, you can use any VAE you like to produce unique aesthetics. Below are the recommended VAEs that you can use with this model to tweak a unique output.

kl-f8-anime2 VAE (for anime)

anything VAE aka orangemix VAE (for anime)

blessed VAE (for anime)

vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (for realism)

Sample images above were created with simple text prompts around default settings. More detailed prompts will produce much better results. As for text prompts, just let your imagination flow. One thing to take note, adding keywords like realistic, realism, photorealism, photorealistic, hyperrealism, hyper-realistic etc., will make the image more real, and not including any word with real on them will make it look anime.

Settings:

Sampling Method: Euler (realistic) or Euler A (anime)

Sampling Steps: 20 to 30

Resolution: 512x512, 512x768, 768x512

CFG Scale: 4 to 7

Popular Embeddings Used (in the samples):

Easy Negative

Deep Negative

Bad artist Negative embedding

veryBadImageNegative

bad_prompt Negative Embedding

negative_hand Negative Embedding

EnvyBetterHands LoCon

Detail Tweaker LoRA

SXZ Vivid Darkness

Theovercomer8's Contrast Fix

Limitations:

Do use this model within the boundaries of legalities; do not use it to harm people and entities, or any illegal matters. Using this model means that you alone are responsible for any forms of consequences good or bad, and the author has no liabilities. We all know that AI models can produce both safe and unsafe images for work, so be very responsible. For all other matters do read the CreativeML-OpenRail-M license. Other than that, enjoy using this model and I hope this will help you in your endeavors as an artist.

Support:

First of all, thank you for patronizing this model; it means my efforts didn't go to waste. My goal is to produce more free tools not just for myself and my work, but for others too. Your generosity will go more than a mile. Also, as an artist, writer, programmer, and overall freelancer, I accept commission job. Thank you so much for your support!

items.name: 日系场景/Japanese scene illustration/日系シーンイラストです/生活感 Lora
items.description:
大家好，我是chosen鲷，这次带来的是日系场景的Lora模型。

训练集是精选的p站上面的一些典型的日系场景插画以及许多日系的游戏原画，目的是想要训练一个带有日系风格特点的厚涂笔触的模型，非常适合做一些游戏的场景设计，以及一些生活感的插图。这个模型可以无tag抽卡，直写上，大家可以根据自己需要尝试，横版竖版均可，分辨率越大越好，在你显卡不爆炸的基础下尽可能大，我的例图是1600*800，然后SD四分法再放大一倍直接3200*1600。关键词Japanese scene，记得高清重绘，重绘方式建议ESRGAN_4X，重绘幅度0.5

建议使用我的chosen impasto或者chosen mix模型,跟其他的大模型相性也还不错，都可以尝试一下，vae搭配蜡笔pastel即可，不建议和偏三次元的原画模型，画风会不搭，我接下来会发布那种3Dcg原画风格的lora，这个建议就做这种日系场景用。例图是能够读取tag的，大家可以尝试一下。

感谢大家的下载使用，如果喜欢的话欢迎关注我，我的bilibili pixiv ID均为chosen鲷，欢迎大家关注我的频道https://space.bilibili.com/3867754?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0，https://www.pixiv.net/users/40911695 谢谢。

Hi, I'm chosen 鲷, and I'm here with a Lora model of the Japanese scene.

The training set is a selection of some typical Japanese scene illustrations on the p website and many Japanese game original paintings, the purpose is to train a model with Japanese style characteristics of thick brush strokes, very suitable for some game scene design, as well as some life sense of illustration. This model can be drawn without tag card, write straight, we can try according to their own needs, horizontal version can be vertical version, the larger the resolution, the better, in your graphics card does not explode under the basis as large as possible, my example is 1600*800, and then SD quarter method and then double directly 3200*1600. Keywords Japanese scene, remember HD redrawing, redrawing method is suggested ESRGAN_4X, redrawing range 0.5

It is recommended to use my chosen impasto or chosen mix model, which has good compatibility with other large models. You can have a try. vae can be combined with pastel, but it is not recommended to use partial three-dimensional original painting model, because the painting style will not match. This suggestion is for this kind of Japanese scene. Example diagram is able to read tag, you can try it.

Thank you for downloading and using, please follow me if you like, my bilibili pixiv ID is chosen Snapper, Welcome to focus on my channel, https://space.bilibili.com/3867754?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0, https://www.pixiv.net/users/40911695, thank you.

こんにちは、chosen鯛です。今回は日系シーンのLoraモデルを持ってきました。

訓練集は選りすぐったpサイト上のいくつかの典型的な日本のシーンのイラストとたくさんの日本のゲームの原画です。目的は1つの日本の風格の特徴の厚いタッチの模型を訓練したいので、とても適していくつかのゲームのシーンのデザインといくつかの生活感のイラストを作ります。このモデルはなしtagカードを引くことができて、まっすぐに書いて、みんなは自分の必要に応じて試すことができて、横版縦版どちらもできて、解像度が大きいほど良くて、あなたのビデオカードが爆発しないようにできるだけ大きくて、私の例の図は1600*800で、それからSD 4分法は直接2倍3200*1600です。キーワードJapanese scene,覚えていますハイビジョン再描画,再描画方式提案ESRGAN_4X,再描画幅0.5

私のchosen impastoやchosen mixモデルを使うことをお勧めします。他の大きなモデルとの相性も悪くありません。すべて試してみてください。vaeとクレヨンpastelを組み合わせることができます。そんな日系シーンにオススメです。例の図ではtagが読めるようになっていますので、試してみてください。

items.description:
Nizomi is a mysterious and enigmatic girl with a captivating presence. With her long, flowing hair that cascades down in a striking shade of greyish purple, she effortlessly stands out in any crowd. Often seen in her school uniform, she exudes an air of elegance and sophistication. Her grey jacket and pleated skirt, paired with a crisp white dress shirt, a black necktie, and black pantyhose, give her a distinctive and polished appearance.

One cannot help but notice Nizomi's physical features, as she possesses a curvaceous figure. Her large breasts and wide hips accentuate her feminine allure. Yet, despite the attention she may attract, she remains stoic and expressionless most of the time.

Nizomi's reserved nature adds to her air of mystery. She is a girl of few words, often preferring silence over idle chatter. Her quiet demeanor gives rise to numerous speculations about her thoughts and feelings, leaving those around her intrigued and curious.

Beneath her reserved exterior, Nizomi possesses a deep well of complexity and untold stories. Her presence commands attention, and those who take the time to unravel her layers may discover a fascinating and multi-faceted individual with hidden depths.

Nizomi's allure lies not only in her striking appearance but also in the enigma that surrounds her. She is a captivating enigma, inviting speculation and leaving others yearning to know more about the girl behind the expressionless facade.

欢迎各位积极返图和评论

For the IP design training model, it can output a 3D style similar to Bubble Mart, or use 3D graphics to transform 2D images, mainly generating Q version cute style.

The V1 version is a native version, while V1.1 is a fusion version with the samaritan3dCartoon model. The former has a more cute style and the Q version, while the latter has stronger applicability.

Steps: 20-30 Recommended: 768 * 102 Sample: DPM++2MKarras

Known for her roles in independent films and blockbusters in both European and Hollywood productions, she has received various accolades, including an Academy Award, a British Academy Film Award, a Golden Globe Award, a European Film Award, a Lumières Award and two César Awards. She became a Knight of the Order of Arts and Letters in France in 2010, and was promoted to Officer in 2016, the same year she was named a Knight of the Legion of Honour. She has served as a spokeswoman for Greenpeace since 2001. She was the face of the Lady Dior handbag for nine years, and since 2020 she is the face of the fragrance Chanel No. 5.

items.name: kanatomimikiru Style
items.description:
This model is based on anything4.5 trained from the picture of kanatomimikiru, and it is recommended to use weights between 0.6 to 0.8.

There have been many controversies about the training and use of art style models, but they are also a difficult part to avoid in the process of AI painting progress.

Therefore, it is recommended to use such art style models as a kind of existence similar to potions, by matching Loras of different art styles with different weights to form images with different styles (although this may lead to bad results, it is worth trying).Alternatively, it can be used to match your favorite character models. Anyway, I hope not to compare it with the artist's own work and make rude remarks, which will harm the community's environment.

At the same time, there are still many problems to be discovered in this model. In short, hope you have a good time.

items.description:
温馨警告

封面图为了骚气些是单独处理过的，只有头像框是用该模型生成，不用尝试该模型生成类似封面图，办不到。

一些症状说明

1. 目前1.0版本的模型出废图率还是比较高的，建议参考附带的例图写提示词。

2. 主要用于方形头像框生成，其他形状的未训练效果不理想。

3. 复制来的关键词出现“Y4PhF”时，需将其改为“头像框”（其他乱码显示的关键词都可删掉）

4. 该模型本身不输出明显的风格特征，有下列症状的都可尝试切换大模型或加入新LORA模型

  • 整体风格不理想

  • 某些局部图形或元素效果不理想，不还原，理解错误等

  • 强烈建议搭配下方推荐的大模型使用

items.name: upskirt below (view) 裙底视角

Update:

v2.0 is trained using generated images from v1.0 and it has better understanding of tags like [pantyhose] or even [nude]. Also, compared with v1.0, v2.0 is not easy to make images distorted.

This LoRA is able to generate the upskirt view of a girl.

The recommended weight is 0.5~1.0.

It dose not well in generating high resolution images, but you can use Hires. fix.

You can also generate the front view by yourself and make these 2 images together (Sample images with 2 views are all made in this way instead of generating directly).

v2.0使用v1.0生成图二次训练，泛化性有很大增强，对[pantyhose],[nude]等tag的理解加深，并且高权重下图片损坏的概率降低很多。

这个LoRA可以用来生成裙底图片。

推荐权重：0.5~1.0。

它不太擅长出大图，如果需要高清图片，推荐用高分辨率修复

你也可以自己另外出一张正面照，然后把它和裙底照拼成一张图（展示的双视角图片都是这样弄的，不是直接生成）

  • You must use the trigger word eldritchtechto activate it, you're in too deep now now there's no going back!

  • u can add cosmic anddark energy to further fuel the creations.

  • when dealing with characters you have the option of adding Wraith and they'll lose whatever humanity they have left!

Usage Tips :

  • healthy LoRA weight range from 0.8 to 1.6

  • get a good from then clean it with hires fix

  • send to img2img to flesh out more details or to strengthen the LoRA even more

  • I recommend checkpoints that works great with generating small details like "revAnimated"

Fun experiments :

  • try LoRA wights past :1 they make for great mystical scenes

  • try figure out how to trigger "cosmic skin effect" at will

  • test with anime characters

  • blend a lethal dosage with other World Morphs

Happy exploration and consider rating ⭐
